    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Noble Connections, Ignoble Intentions</h2><br>The king has summoned you! Recent reports indicate that there's a spy amongst the court magicians. You are the only noble qualified to join them without alerting suspicion so it's left to you to investigate.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353420/extras/6c46583a6ff38962729c1bad17e3397c.avif?t=1750747711\" width=634 height=356 /></span><br><br>Your parents are upset that you, future head of your noble family, do not have a spouse. They demand descendants and, fortunately for them, you're about to meet some high status peers.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353420/extras/fb8848c697f4aa7845b94f5d9ac9c155.avif?t=1750747711\" width=634 height=356 /></span><br><br>Off you go to the join the Court Magicians to capture a spy and a spouse (or more than one)!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353420/extras/e6da1b9911cb1b186c48c64921272716.avif?t=1750747711\" width=634 height=356 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The court has a spy, connect disparate conversations, and capture them for the king.</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353420/extras/2b6d32df9edda5224dc5ff583f602db6.avif?t=1750747711\" width=634 height=356 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353420/extras/e63d4156968279b8ac148b1fa10dcb42.avif?t=1750747711\" width=634 height=356 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353420/extras/2c3445f13e15c4c24f70c3060ae8c3f2.avif?t=1750747711\" width=634 height=356 /></span><br>Pay attention to the details.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Court magicians, connect with them through conversation, and capture their hearts.</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353420/extras/0208850824064b7a3f22ddb792530c70.avif?t=1750747711\" width=634 height=356 /></span><br>Talk to the Court Magicians.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353420/extras/62f1d30ff220c5359b28f87853159c38.avif?t=1750747711\" width=634 height=356 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353420/extras/6b9d172335e01e10dfdc7b255a1d135e.avif?t=1750747711\" width=634 height=356 /></span><br>Make connections...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353420/extras/1f271f97b175bf04d056aa775a94b322.avif?t=1750747711\" width=634 height=356 /></span><br>Capture hearts.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353420/extras/eb77d6709e18bec2c7cf16a06fca10ca.avif?t=1750747711\" width=634 height=356 /></span><br>Or get rejections.<br><br>Some people are harder to court than others as their personalities and circumstances will vary.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Your Own Story</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353420/extras/28d46f180b24165de30f3828cc04cfef.avif?t=1750747711\" width=634 height=356 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353420/extras/43f151023372835207d5efd87fa5ba7b.avif?t=1750747711\" width=634 height=356 /></span><br><strong>Every play through is unique with:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Different characters featuring their own appearance, personalities, and histories.<br></li><li>A variety of events move the plot forward.<br></li><li>Multiple endings from romantic to tragic.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353420/extras/0349ed4ae0c4c5d2b477a79ebae2f17c.avif?t=1750747711\" width=634 height=356 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>One conversation mechanic that simultaneously supports romantic interactions and thrilling deductions!<br></li><li>Uniquely generated plotlines and a scoring system add replay value.<br></li><li>Play the way that you want:<br>      Be romantic and find your one-true-love.<br>      Focus only on the investigation if you don't care to flirt.<br>      Marry all of your suitors (maybe avoid bad actors).</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353420/extras/c3e4c5e96019c1ce1890d90b96d1a220.avif?t=1750747711\" width=634 height=356 /></span>",
